SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[CustomerId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[PaymentStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [c].[UserId], [c].[Address], [c].[Email], [c].[FirstName], [c].[LastName], [c].[PhoneNumber], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductId], [s].[Quantity], [s].[Id0], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Description], [s].[ImageUrl], [s].[Name], [s].[Price0], [s].[Stock], [s].[Id1], [s].[Description0], [s].[Name0]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Price], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[Stock], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[Description] AS [Description0], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [c].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[Id0]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[CustomerId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[PaymentStatus], [o].[TotalAmount], [c].[UserId], [c].[Address], [c].[Email], [c].[FirstName], [c].[LastName], [c].[PhoneNumber], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductId], [s].[Quantity], [s].[Id0], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Description], [s].[ImageUrl], [s].[Name], [s].[Price0], [s].[Stock], [s].[Id1], [s].[Description0], [s].[Name0]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Price], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[Quantity], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[Stock], [c0].[Id] AS [Id1], [c0].[Description] AS [Description0], [c0].[Name] AS [Name0]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [c].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[Id0]
